node.text:
Today I am sharing tips about everything Thanksgiving in partnership with the incredible @voluspacandles and @cfadesigngroup to make it more memorable than ever!

With unprecedented times surrounding us this year, our place settings will be limited but that doesn’t mean that it still can’t be special! I hope this inspires you to continue to create memories around the table with your immediate loved ones!❤️

Wishing you all a safe and memorable Thanksgiving! I am thankful for my health and family! What are you thankful for? 🥰

Special thanks to @voluspacandles and @cfadesigngroup for their incredible partnership and making this possible! My entire centerpiece featuring the gorgeous Magnolia arrangements and driftwood are from @cfadesigngroup ✨

Get the look! Take advantage of @cfadesigngroup Thanksgiving and Black Friday sale going on right now and receive 15% off their stunning faux florals for a limited time!!

Eid Mubarak to all those celebrating from my family to yours! 🥰 

Have you tried the viral pasta chips yet? #ad 

So I finally tried the famous air fried pasta chips thanks to @walmart and my goodness did they turn out scrumptiously crispy and the hubby even approved! ☺️ See the recipe below.

I am truly impressed by the quality of all of my unique home decor finds and kitchen appliances I’ve shared in this video of which some are sold exclusively on Walmart.com and so budget friendly! 

I also love the free 2 day shipping option on everything $35 and over delivered right to your doorstep. #walmarthome
#wowandnow 

Follow me on @shop.ltk and be sure to check out my stories where I will be linking all my incredible finds in this video from @walmart on @ltk.home app!

Wishing you all a blessed Eid surrounded by loved ones! Are you inspired?! 🥰

Ingredients and recipe were inspired by Yumna Jawad. 

📝For the Pasta Chips

8 ounces rigatoni pasta
1 tablespoon olive oil
3 tablespoons freshly grated Parmesan cheese
½ teaspoon Italian seasoning
½ teaspoon garlic powder
Kosher salt
Freshly ground black pepper

📝For the Whipped Feta Dip

4 ounces crumbled feta cheese
2 ounces Greek yogurt
1 garlic clove
2 tablespoons olive oil
